mdRecord.dcterms:title: Jennington, I. W. to Pierpont, Francis Harrison
mdRecord.dcterms:creator: Jennington, I. W.
mdRecord.dcterms:description: Gov FH Peirpoint [Francis H. Pierpont] Wheeling Aug 186. By Telegraph from Fairmont 186. I am in receipt of papers. Has your proclamation of the twenty ninth 29th superceded service notices or must I proceed & to what counties first instructions and law differ as to counties I. W. Jennington 32a101pd

Fairmont, (West) Virginia

Pierpont, Francis Harrison
